Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:33.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:53.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:59.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:08.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:14.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:19.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:27.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:33.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:36.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:43.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:49.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達目的地了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 HSR3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打過去了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠哉的什麼都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁這空檔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第七戰來臨前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 武八
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是HSR3耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是風見隼人先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以請你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起參加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十九話 挑戰!火焰熱球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開什麼玩笑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人他還要參加重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七戰世界冠軍杯車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼危險的二流車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以叫隼人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的知道火焰熱球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的車賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是超過限制速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比賽規則的車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還常常鬧出人命來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加比賽贏得冠軍才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生的車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經全都看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你的技術絕對沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界冠軍杯車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟火焰熱球雖然都是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是性質完全不同呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜聽他說完 良平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你先告訴我們詳情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽的主辦者了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我爸爸的兩個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不能原諒爸爸他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們把賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都視為一場賭博的道具 太沒有人性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們居然把車賽中毀壞的車子數量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡人數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是誰撞壞別人車子最好等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都當做賭博的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次…也是…也是同樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次算我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦傑那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定恨得咬牙切齒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 什麼事讓你大聲小叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再花錢舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太興奮對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花錢拿人的性命來玩樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做…這樣做真的太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些賽車手是為了得到獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自願拿性命來開玩笑參賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿這些人的性命賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼地方不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你們做的事就是不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該是那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這麼講的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你看怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟爸爸睹一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的都不瞭解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說呀 你跟爸爸賭賭看 這一次火焰熱球車賽的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你選的賽車手贏得了冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那爸爸就聽你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不再花錢舉辦車賽讓那些亡命之徒來比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 既然你都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就彼此約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們就這麼約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有錢人拿這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做娛樂真是太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這明明就是對賽車的侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情也跟良平的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對艾蓮娜不太好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最讓我生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們居然對賽車沒有半點感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情我都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平跟美樹他們兩個都說的很對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得他們真的是很不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要參加火焰熱球車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿到冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓艾蓮娜的爸爸跟朋友都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的車賽該是什麼樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以車隊代理人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許你去參加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 車子怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了應付即將來到的非洲杯車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級阿斯拉達正在接受調整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就交給我辦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在車賽前的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撥時間一點一點的修理起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把電腦系統裝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就能夠跑得跟新車子一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在於阿斯拉達了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的話我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力支持你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然阿斯拉達已經答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒有任何問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們大家 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 幸好我沒有白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的蠻意外的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天怎麼會這麼爽快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是為了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞成廢鐵才製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些主辦人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讓人不愉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對 阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類應該對車子更有愛心才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是HSR3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多指教 阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在跟阿斯拉達講話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在看到的這一台HSR3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可跟其它車子的電腦系統對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 馬上把電腦系統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移到舊的車身去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次的車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會撞壞幾台車子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼關係反正賭要賭大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來賭賭看看死幾個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蠻有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就睹那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從比賽開始到終點結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一段時間可以刺激刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛快要移不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們現在來做個預定表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 小姐打電話給您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到火焰熱球車賽的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定可以贏得冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼跟女兒有個小約定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 跟小姐的約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應他如果他挑選的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這次的比賽裏面拿到冠軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不再出錢舉辦賭博了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫風見隼人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是拿到高智能方程式英國冠軍杯的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才型的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且才只有十四歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一你輸了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也再沒辦法玩遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數太少的話玩起來就沒趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽是沒有生命保證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無規則的危險賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四歲的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得出什麼事來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦系統已經連結好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 新介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是可以帶一名嚮導嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對計算時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟賽程的測定都很有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會對你很有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實好久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想跟你一起比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚮導的話 由我來當最適合了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一途中機器發生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我修理就最方便不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了 美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要去耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽又不是去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可不可以請你帶我一起去比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 你的心情我很瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這場車賽很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不想讓隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我而冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己卻躲在一旁觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車賽的路程我全部都很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們別看我是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我將來也想當賽車選手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是很複雜的故障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我也能夠幫忙修理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我曾跟加賀玩過碰撞賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼HSR3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你們幫照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜小姐就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧 HSR3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一種懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些賽車的裝備全部都好誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於車子沒有硬性規定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能搭自己喜歡的車子出場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要參這個車賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你現在已經漸漸的知道錢的好處了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一次跟我連手參加碰撞車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了你不少自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要參加這場比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的獎金多得像磁鐵一樣的吸引著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做艾蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隼人的嚮導 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在什麼地方碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼可愛的女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂想了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你竟然隱瞞我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說 告訴我 快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位不要命的賽車手們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你們來參加這一次的火焰熱球車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次的賽程是從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧運的發源地雅典開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到巴黎的凱旋門為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快到達的人就算贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼老是把麻煩攪在身上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事情都這樣了 總不能放著不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就幫你一把好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個車賽的重點就在於
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些暴力傾向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意的傢伙首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開黑色車子的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是像摔跤選手的那個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個眼神很邪惡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是這車賽的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一群為了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不擇手段的骯髒傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他們跟在你後面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要特別小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99號參賽者 加賀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請到出發位置準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點我忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力支持你讓你得勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你贏了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎金要分我一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 我要是贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎金就全都送給你 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是欣賞你這一點 既大方又乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀先生不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算自動棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆的開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利德這次應該不會輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這一次再輸了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就等於連輸三次給蓋本了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始來享受我們的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬我們的友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 爸爸做夢也有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會跟你睹一場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 現在利用衛星跟大家取得連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿斯拉達衛星傳來的連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車身跟電腦系統已經完美的連結在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎運轉情況也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 隼人他們就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的東西 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就在發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被他打敗了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就是戰場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 你要坐好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個撞上就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加速了 坐穩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是比賽才剛開始不久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋滑風扇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼比賽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意後方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一輛重型貨櫃車接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個車子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢擋住我去路的人通通都該死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快給我閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不你不順眼 如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 使用推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進器啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎倒數計時到臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 你要坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺有一手的嘛 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 他追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 沒辦法逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路完全被堵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推進器關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得在這個地方下場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蓮娜 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擋我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼賽車呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是阿斯拉達GSX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風見隼人以前開的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當的了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的表現還真不像一個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛這輛車子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是艾蓮娜選上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰熱球車賽現在才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 阿斯拉達 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

